CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 12, 1962, pg. 14 reads: "Outstanding - John H. Adams is shown with his "The New Negro Directory," an outstanding and significant book crammed full of facts on Pittsburgh's Negro businessmen. The book was published this week. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Portrait of John H. Adams wearing moustache and horizontally striped necktie, holding his book titled "The New Negro Directory", standing on sidewalk next to brick building
